    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BITE-SIZED, BULLET-HELL, ROGUE-LIKE, SCORE-ATTACK, TWIN-STICK!</strong></h2><br>Get into the research lab, throw black holes, try to survive, defeat the final boss, and get to the top of the leaderboards! Nebula's Descent is a game made by 8 university students over 10 weeks for the Ubisoft Game Lab competition. <br><br>Nebula's Descent features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Steam Leaderboards where you can compete with your friends and the world<br></li><li> 19 rooms with 7 enemy spawn patterns each<br></li><li> Bullet Hell Gameplay<br></li><li> A Final Boss<br></li><li> Points-based continue system, allowing anyone to finish the game while rewarding successful players with better scores<br></li><li> Blackhole Grenade and Box Spawn combat abilities<br></li><li> Points-based upgrade system where you can enhance your weapon, health or abilities<br></li><li> Colorful, bright graphics with tons of particles and a unique style<br></li><li> Great Optimization.</li></ul>",
